BT
/F1 11 Tf
1 0 0 1 50 742 Tm (That is why the unit problem matters. It is not a semantic nuisance. It is a mechanism by) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 728 Tm (which technical shorthand becomes scientific distortion and then institutional) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 714 Tm (misgovernance.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 700 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 686 Tm (## 8. Toward Unit-Aware Agent Science) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 672 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 658 Tm (A more disciplined field would begin by declaring its unit explicitly.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 644 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 630 Tm (At minimum, serious reporting on agent systems should distinguish among:) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 616 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 602 Tm (1. **Base model**) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 588 Tm (2. **Workflow**) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 574 Tm (3. **Harness and tool layer**) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 560 Tm (4. **Persistence and memory layer**) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 546 Tm (5. **Budget regime**) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 532 Tm (6. **Execution environment**) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 518 Tm (7. **Oversight and governance structure**) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 504 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 490 Tm (This should not remain a vague recommendation. A unit-aware agent science should adopt at) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 476 Tm (least four working norms.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 462 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 448 Tm (### 8.1 Declare the unit of claim) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 434 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 420 Tm (Every serious claim should specify whether it is about the model, the workflow-conditioned) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 406 Tm (system, the harness, the action system, or some other layer.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 392 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 378 Tm (### 8.2 Refuse cross-paper comparison when units silently differ) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 364 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 350 Tm (If two papers compare "agent performance" but one studies a model-with-tools scaffold and) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 336 Tm (the other studies a persistent, approval-gated action system, the comparison should be) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 322 Tm (treated as structurally weak unless units are normalized or differences are made explicit.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 308 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 294 Tm (### 8.3 Separate explanation from intervention) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 280 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 266 Tm (What explains a property and where leverage over that property lives may differ. Reports) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 252 Tm (should not assume explanatory bearer and intervention target are the same.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 238 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 224 Tm (### 8.4 Disclose the governed object in institutional claims) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 210 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 196 Tm (Claims about safety, oversight, supervision, compliance, or accountability should state what) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 182 Tm (assembled object they actually refer to.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 168 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 154 Tm (Taken together, these norms amount to a modest but real disciplinary proposal: stop letting) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 140 Tm ("the model" function as a universal placeholder when the practical phenomenon is clearly) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 126 Tm (distributed across a larger system.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 112 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 98 Tm (This is not only a corrective. It is also an opportunity. Once units are declared more) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 84 Tm (carefully, comparisons become more honest, explanations become more portable, interventions) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 70 Tm (become more targeted, and governance claims become easier to audit. In that sense, unit-) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 56 Tm (aware agent science is not just a defensive cleanup. It is one path toward a more cumulative) Tj
ET
endstream
